snippet.title: The Deer - Steam gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
"The Deer" is an educational inter­ac­tive expe­ri­ence for children for Steam platform http://store.steampowered.com/app/400240/

You'll interpred an ancient Deer during the Pleistocene epoch and you'll discover everything about this marvelous era.

Unfortunately there were no T-Rexes during this age since were already extinct millions of years before.
